.DT
query_door_type
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_door_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_door_type -  This method returns information about the door type, the door has extra information associated with it than the standard exit type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed query_door_type(string type,
string direc,
mixed dest)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the door
%^BOLD%^direc%^RESET%^ - the direction the door points
%^BOLD%^dest%^RESET%^ - the destination of the door
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the door type array of information

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/room_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns information about the door type, the door has
extra information associated with it than the standard exit type.
This function does a double job of trying to find the corresponding
door on the other side of the room.
.EP

